## PASOS PARA EL SETUP DE EL Urdf"" 

- compilar el paquete que queremos 

cd ~/ws_moveit
colcon build --packages-select dummy_arm2_description
source install/setup.zsh

- correr el setup de moveIt 
export QT_QPA_PLATFORM=xcb      # si da error de entorno grafico agregar esta linea                       
ros2 launch moveit_setup_assistant setup_assistant.launch.py  

Subir archivo .xacro
load files 

## Comenzar con la confiiguracion 

start screen :
- check collision

Self-collision:
- generate collision matrix
- matrix view. In this step u can see if the components can made a collition(check) or not (uncheck)

Virtual joints: 
empty 

Planning Groups:
You can made sub groups like the body of the arm and the hand 

Group default planner: RRTConnect 

add Kin.chain: in this case you select de base_link and the top link of the group 

Robot Poses: 
you can define some defalut poses like home 

Define End Efferctors 

if u have a gripper u can upload some states of this, like close or open. 

Pasive joints
mechanics joints.
the robot cant control them.
ros2_control & ROS2 Controllers & moveit controllers made de auto config 

Perception :
 if uf havve a cloud points 
 
 agregar limites de velociad en joints 
 
 lanzar paquete 

source install/setup.zsh
ros2 launch dummy_arm2_moveit_config demo.launch.py


controllers 

# Cargar individualmente
ros2 control load_controller joint_state_broadcaster
ros2 control load_controller manipulator_controller

# O cargar ambos
ros2 control load_controller joint_state_broadcaster manipulator_controller

 
# configuracion

ros2 service call /controller_manager/configure_controller controller_manager_msgs/srv/ConfigureController '{name: "joint_state_broadcaster"}'
ros2 service call /controller_manager/configure_controller controller_manager_msgs/srv/ConfigureController '{name: "manipulator_controller"}'



ros2 launch basic_arm2_moveit_config democontrol.launch.py 
  ros2 topic pub /manipulator_controller/joint_trajectory trajectory_msgs/msg/JointTrajectory "{
  joint_names: ['rev_1', 'rev_2', 'rev_3'],
  points: [{positions: [10.0, 20.0, 30.0], time_from_start: {sec: 1}}]
}"



cd ~/microros_ws
sros
ros2 run micro_ros_agent micro_ros_agent serial --dev /dev/ttyACM0

ros2 topic pub -1  /motor_angles std_msgs/Int32MultiArray "data: [0, 360, 0]"

puente 
